      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum linear-elastic model with frictional contact justified by literature and prior validation studies for metallic spinal implant constructs under quasi-static loading.",
      "rationale": "The pedicle screw and rod are modeled as Ti-6Al-4V linear-elastic continua. Frictional contact at screw-rod interface (mu=0.2) is consistent with published cadaveric and bench characterization. Model form is appropriate for quasi-static compression-bending within the elastic regime."
