      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric dimensions sourced from manufacturer data sheets and measured specimen dimensions; uncertainty in inputs quantified and propagated.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), Poisson ratio (0.34), and yield strength (880 MPa) for Ti-6Al-4V taken from ASTM F136 and confirmed by manufacturer certificate of conformance. Geometric dimensions measured on five representative screws; CV < 0.5%. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (500 samples)."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
