      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were drawn from a single production lot and tested across two independent laboratories (n=6 and n=5). Dimensional inspection confirmed all specimens within ±0.05 mm of nominal. Full traceability chain documented."
