      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA boundary conditions and loading protocol are demonstrably equivalent to ASTM F1717 test fixture geometry and applied loads; fixture compliance accounted for.",
      "rationale": "The ASTM F1717 test fixture geometry was reproduced in the FEA model from manufacturer drawings. Applied displacement boundary conditions match the actuator displacement protocol. Load cell and actuator compliance were measured and incorporated as spring elements. Input equivalency confirmed by sensitivity analysis."
