      "acceptanceCriteria": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) within 10% of experimental mean; E/uval < 1.96 for each QoI.",
      "rationale": "FEA predictions: stiffness 187 N/mm (exp. mean 183 N/mm, 2.2% diff); yield force 412 N (exp. mean 405 N, 1.7% diff); force at 40 mm 680 N (exp. mean 671 N, 1.3% diff). E/uval values: 0.41, 0.38, 0.29. All acceptance criteria met across both laboratories."
